{"article_id":"2yj8gvEsDMTYGrm4","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Documents confirm","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"Hillary Clinton was using her secret email server before the March 18 start date","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"she previously claimed ,","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"and the State Department had access to some of the messages all along","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"but didn ' t notice ,","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"a conservative legal watchdog said Thursday .","depth":4},{"id":6,"text":"Judicial Watch ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"which has filed a host of lawsuits","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"to try to pry loose Mrs. Clinton ' s emails ,","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"released a Feb. 13 exchange between Mrs. Clinton , the new secretary of state , and aide Cheryl Mills","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"concerning Mrs. Clinton ' s desire for a secure BlackBerry","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"to handle classified email traffic .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"Last year , Mrs. Clinton indicated","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"she started using her secret account on the clintonemail.com server","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"she kept at her home in New York in March ,","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"two months after she was sworn in as secretary .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"But the email discovery confirms reports last year","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that she was using the account before that date .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"She emailed David H. Petraeus ,","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"who was serving as CIA director ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"from her secret account that January .","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"The email","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"released Thursday by Judicial Watch","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"was sent to Ms. Mills at her official State Department address ,","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"meaning the department has had it in its possession all along","depth":8},{"id":25,"text":"- though it did not provide it to the conservative legal group until last week .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"\" It ' s another dirty little secret","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that the State Department hoped","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"nobody would notice , \"","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"said Tom Fitton , president of Judicial Watch ,","depth":8},{"id":30,"text":"who has filed a lawsuit","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"demanding","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"that the department go back and search for more such emails .","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Mrs. Clinton had said","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"all of the official record emails from her first two months as secretary ,","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"which she was required by law to store and leave in the department archives ,","depth":7},{"id":36,"text":"are no longer available to her .","depth":6},{"id":37,"text":"But the Mills email shows","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"the State Department itself may be sitting on a number of those messages .","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"The department did not comment on","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"whether it would go back to look for more Clinton emails .","depth":5},{"id":41,"text":"Last month , it finished processing some 30,000 messages","depth":5},{"id":42,"text":"Mrs. Clinton did return to the government","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"nearly two years after she left office .","depth":6},{"id":44,"text":"Mrs. Clinton ' s presidential campaign didn ' t respond to a request","depth":3},{"id":45,"text":"seeking comment on the discrepancy in her email use .","depth":3},{"id":46,"text":"The State Department has acknowledged gaps in records of Mrs. Clinton ' s communications","depth":5},{"id":47,"text":"- particularly at the start of her tenure .","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"An official said Thursday","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"that the department is relying on Mrs. Clinton ' s own representations about her account use .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"\" Secretary Clinton and her team have indicated","depth":7},{"id":51,"text":"that they provided the department with all work-related emails in her possession from her time at the department , \"","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"the official said .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"The FBI and the State Department ' s inspector general are looking into Mrs. Clinton ' s email server and whether classified information was sent or received .","depth":4},{"id":54,"text":"Mrs. Clinton initially said","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"no classified business was transacted ,","depth":8},{"id":56,"text":"but revised her statement","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"to say","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"none of the information was marked classified at the time","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"she first handled it .","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"A number of emails have shown , however ,","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"that she was aware of the potential","depth":8},{"id":62,"text":"for classified information to come across her email .","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"The messages","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"released Thursday by Judicial Watch","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"detail the efforts","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"her team made","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"to try to get a secure BlackBerry device from the National Security Agency .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"\" The email shows","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"there ' s no doubt","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"Mrs. Clinton was involved in the BlackBerry matter ,","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"and everything","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"her staff knew ,","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"she knew","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"- meaning the BlackBerrys weren ' t secure ,","depth":9},{"id":75,"text":"and she shouldn ' t be using them , \"","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"Mr. Fitton said .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":153,"left":120,"right":152,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":109,"right":119,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":82,"right":108,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":82,"left":81,"right":5,"relation"